Woodhaven Boulevard, at 65th Avenue. Shown are two views of the area, looking southeastward, in the vicinity of St. John Cemetery. Woodhaven Boulevard is the former Trotting Course Lane.

View 1: Eugene L. Armbruster Collection 1923

View 2: P. L. Sperr June 29, 1936
